  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C.",
    "Combine flour, sugar and salt in a bowl.",
    "Add butter and mix until the mixture resembles coarse breadcrumbs.",
    "Mix branston-pickle, orange zest, orange juice and lemon juice in a separate bowl.",
    "Mix in eggs and milk, then stir in vanilla extract.",
    "Mix in the branston-pickle mixture with the breadcrumb mixture.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and top with more breadcrumbs and a drizzle of infuse-oil.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Serve warm, topped with additional branston-pickle and crumbly breadcrumbs.",
    "Let it rest for 10 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve and enjoy!"
